## Responsiveness Rules:
- Design mobile-first layouts
- Ensure UI works across mobile, tablet and desktop
- Use responsive flexbox and grid layout
- Avoid fixed width whenever possible
- Maintain proper alignment across screeen size

## Mobile UI Rules:
- Ensure Buttons are touch friendly
- Prevent horizontal scrolling
- Keep text readable on smaller screen

## Layout Rules 
- Use Flexbox for one-dimensional layout
- Use CSS Grid for complex layouts
- Prefer percentage(%) and Relative units(rem) over fixed pixels
